    JsonTranslator, XmlDocumentTranslator, VariableTranslator

    public class YamlTranslator
extends DocumentReferenceTranslator
implements XmlDocumentTranslator, JsonTranslator
    By convention, the first line of serialized yaml is a comment that declares the type (class name) of the JavaBean object. Implements XmlDocumentTranslator only for serializing as ExecutionPlan (TODO fix that).
